55:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":["一如既往，身边很多非常优秀的同事一直在给我注入正能量，有年幼的PM、低调的总监、牛逼的Android Dev、大师级的Sponsor、战斗机型的QA。跟一群优秀的人在一起工作久了，自己也在向优秀靠近，感谢有你们，感谢 ",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://thoughtworks.com/","className":"text-primary hover:underline break-all","children":"ThoughtWorks"}]," 这个大家庭。"]}]
56:["$","hr",null,{"className":"my-8 border-border"}]
57:["$","h2",null,{"id":"给自己一个赞","className":"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-3 scroll-mt-24","children":"给自己一个赞"}]
58:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"2016，已成为历史，这一年，努力着，进步着，也一直坚持健身，同时跟自己喜欢的女孩一起变得越来越好，给自己一个赞。"}]
59:["$","hr",null,{"className":"my-8 border-border"}]
5a:["$","h2",null,{"id":"keep-2017","className":"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-3 scroll-mt-24","children":"Keep 2017"}]
